description: Suspended on cords, these tiles are excellent portable training devices, allowing you to do  pull-ups, lock-offs and dead hangs to stay in condition through the winter. Each hold includes a deep jug on top, a four-finger pocket, a four-finger flat edge, and a three-finger pocket.Made of textured polyester resin.Designed to allow rotation of joints to prevent injury.CNC-milled, for perfect symmetry.Suspension holes are now run deeper for better durability.Sorry, no colour choice.
name: Metolius Rock Rings 3D
